T05:30:38.000Z","msg":"電視播緊衛斯理，屋企個homepod係咁彈出黎講野"},{"pid":"5e05b5816ba710bb84d15977b011dc11cc533b5c","tid":663630,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T06:29:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33b0e5ecb2424a23c8c449a7ffa804bb9df2740c","tid":663630,"uid":134437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T07:09:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.inside.com.tw/2016/11/08/siri-smart\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inside.com.tw%2F2016%2F11%2F08%2Fsiri-smart&d=9NWIzGp2NUhs3HN07PqVVNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=6c15999d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inside.com.tw/2016/11/08/siri-smart</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inside.com.tw/2017/05/22/siri-vs-google-assistant-on-iphone\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inside.com.tw%2F2017%2F05%2F22%2Fsiri-vs-google-assistant-on-iphone&d=9NWIzGp2NUhs3HN07PqVVNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=62eeb27a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inside.com.tw/2017/05/22/siri-vs-google-assistant-on-iphone</a>"},{"pid":"90f7b32af484481aa234a87f104eda487430063e","tid":663630,"uid":134437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33b0e5ecb2424a23c8c449a7ffa804bb9df2740c","tid":663630,"uid":134437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T07:09:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.inside.com.tw/2016/11/08/siri-smart\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inside.com.tw%2F2016%2F11%2F08%2Fsiri-smart&d=9NWIzGp2NUhs3HN07PqVVNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=6c15999d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inside.com.tw/2016/11/08/siri-smart</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inside.com.tw/2017/05/22/siri-vs-google-assistant-on-iphone\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inside.com.tw%2F2017%2F05%2F22%2Fsiri-vs-google-assistant-on-iphone&d=9NWIzGp2NUhs3HN07PqVVNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=62eeb27a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inside.com.tw/2017/05/22/siri-vs-google-assistant-on-iphone</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T07:10:25.000Z","msg":"上述結論並不出乎意料。在全球四大語音助手中，微軟的 Cortana 和蘋果 Siri 目前處於落後水平，Google Assistant 和亞馬遜 Alexa 已經進入了前段班，而且 Alexa 作為後起之秀追趕得十分凶猛，也被大量的第三方硬體廠商植入了自己的設備中。<br />\n<br />\n眾所周知的是，蘋果歷史上對於最新科技的研發並不熱衷，去年 100 億美元的研發開支創下公司紀錄，但僅僅是三星電子的三分之一，在科技公司研發支出榜單中，蘋果並未進入前十名。<br />\n<br />\n研發上的忽視，導致蘋果在人工智慧、機器學習領域技術積累不足，直接影響到了 Siri 的智商。好在蘋果已經意識到了問題所在，已經在美國西雅圖市設立了人工智慧研發中心，使命之一就是提高 Siri 的智商，縮小和產業領先者的差距。<br />\n<br />\n過去媒體已經針對語音助手進行過許多測試，結果發現在上下文識別（即根據用戶之前說過的話，來理解最新說的一句話）方面，蘋果 Siri 和 Google Assistant 存在明顯一段距離。"},{"pid":"c2f09ce7ab97837b1aad60673131857d0c784b63","tid":663630,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T07:59:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"03fcc606fa26ee51c87f2d1cb3535488a9898601","tid":663630,"uid":22535,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T08:07:36.000Z","msg":"講幫我呀，同我做咩咩，都唔識。要用好正規中文先識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，成個低能仔，諗緊買隻 google home ，定 alexa 返黎試下。"}]}